@NODE intro.fp
@TITLE "Introduction"
@SMARTWRAP
@WORDWRAP
This can replace the MagicWB daemon. It pre-allocates the specified pens before
the Workbench« screen is opened.
@{CODE}
@ENDNODE

@NODE install.fp
@TITLE "Installation"
@SMARTWRAP
@WORDWRAP
Just copy the binary to a location in your path (i.e. C:).
Then add this line to your S:user-startup file:
@{CODE}
run >NIL: ForcePens 4 123 123 123 5 175 175 175 6 170 144 124 7 255 169 151 QUIET


Note: these values are the standard MWB colors you can find in the
"Click Me For Colors" files in MWB distribution packages.
@ENDNODE

@NODE usage.fp
@TITLE "Usage"
@SMARTWRAP
@WORDWRAP
No need to describe, see @{"Installation" link install.fp} instead!
@{CODE}
@ENDNODE

